    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Genasi are usually humanoids with partial elemental ancestry. Sometimes a genasi is created by fusing a humanoid with elemental magic. While they are mortal, and may not have been born on one of the elemental planes, they nonetheless bear many traits of elemental creatures.\u00a0Fire genasi are usually the descendants of mortals and efreeti. They can harmlessly ignite their hair, eyes, or other body parts, and often bear other signs of their elemental lineage, such as a burnt smell, red skin, or flame-like hair.</p><p><strong>Type:</strong>\u00a0&amp;Reference[Elemental]{Elemental}</p><p><strong>Size:</strong> Medium or Small</p><p><strong>Walking Speed:</strong>\u00a030 ft.</p><p><strong>Senses:</strong>\u00a0&amp;Reference[Darkvision] 60 ft.</p><p><strong>Cantrips</strong>:\u00a0<em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.D8IuKqy7kayCCO15]{Produce Flame}</em></p><p><strong>Damage Resistance</strong>: &amp;reference[Fire]</p><p><strong>Language</strong>:\u00a0You can read and write @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-rules.JournalEntry.5l8QNlgPDPOHpGID.JournalEntryPage.VZggCkMcvhk0X5Xj#primordial]{Primordial} and speak its Ignan dialect.</p><p>\u200b</p><p><em>In the world of Elkan, genasi are rare except in regions with an active portal to one of the elemental planes. Each of the elemental planes has one major gateway that allows travelers to move between planes. Each of these portals are either remote, guarded, or difficult to reach. Fire genasi in Elkan are rare. The main entrance to the Elemental Plane of Fire, the Solar portal platform known as Sol, is the planet's source of sunlight, and angels control traffic through that portal strictly. Genasi are often the children of summoned elementals, or mortal planar travelers who had affairs while in the Plane of Fire.</em>\u00a0</p>",
